  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this top down bullet hell with endless zombies, survive as long as you can against a perpetually overwhelming zombie horde. Luckily, you can find an arsenal of high-powered weaponry to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/736464961b82906bd1b9c4b627e46c2d.poster.avif?t=1737056076\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/736464961b82906bd1b9c4b627e46c2d.webm?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/736464961b82906bd1b9c4b627e46c2d.mp4?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game consists of a variety of weapons and characters across all runs, with maps & power-up builds used to differentiate each run. Save humanity and see how long you can live against the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/30b4c9202f7415286c15a2850edd2e71.poster.avif?t=1737056076\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/30b4c9202f7415286c15a2850edd2e71.webm?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/30b4c9202f7415286c15a2850edd2e71.mp4?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>GPU-Driven technology allowing an impressive sum of zombies on-screen while keeping the frame-rate smooth</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VR and desktop support</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Progression both in and out of runs</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Level-up your run by buying & upgrading power-ups at the shop</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Collect coins by destroying the horde and saving humans</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Quick Sessions: Unlimited time-length with fast-paced ramp-up</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/4d008c92ec0419d4a02d85a049739359.avif?t=1737056076\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras_big/4d008c92ec0419d4a02d85a049739359.avif?t=1737056076 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this top down bullet hell with endless zombies, survive as long as you can against a perpetually overwhelming zombie horde. Luckily, you can find an arsenal of high-powered weaponry to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/736464961b82906bd1b9c4b627e46c2d.poster.avif?t=1737056076\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/736464961b82906bd1b9c4b627e46c2d.webm?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/736464961b82906bd1b9c4b627e46c2d.mp4?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game consists of a variety of weapons and characters across all runs, with maps & power-up builds used to differentiate each run. Save humanity and see how long you can live against the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/30b4c9202f7415286c15a2850edd2e71.poster.avif?t=1737056076\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/30b4c9202f7415286c15a2850edd2e71.webm?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/30b4c9202f7415286c15a2850edd2e71.mp4?t=1737056076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>GPU-Driven technology allowing an impressive sum of zombies on-screen while keeping the frame-rate smooth</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VR and desktop support</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Progression both in and out of runs</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Level-up your run by buying & upgrading power-ups at the shop</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Collect coins by destroying the horde and saving humans</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Quick Sessions: Unlimited time-length with fast-paced ramp-up</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/4d008c92ec0419d4a02d85a049739359.avif?t=1737056076\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras_big/4d008c92ec0419d4a02d85a049739359.avif?t=1737056076 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul>",
